div></div></div></details><details class="sc-dGVrNp kIZjuh pf-217_" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content.Wrapper"><summary><div class="sc-deEcaK pLXxN pf-218_ pf-anchor pf-header-item-wrapper" data-header-id="162a7c44-3e9e-4530-9ea4-80a05e71ebcd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Header"><svg class="pf-accordion-icon pfa-chevron-right pfa-arrow" style="width:auto;fill:currentcolor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 320 512"><path d="M278.6 233.4c12.5 12.5 12.5 32.8 0 45.3l-160 160c-12.5 12.5-32.8 12.5-45.3 0s-12.5-32.8 0-45.3L210.7 256 73.4 118.6c-12.5-12.5-12.5-32.8 0-45.3s32.8-12.5 45.3 0l160 160z"></path></svg><span>Was ist im Set enthalten?</span></div></summary><div class="sc-lmEGMn dTrJQN pf-220_ pf-accordion-body" data-pf-expandable="true" data-pf-type="Accordion3.Content"><div class="pf-accordion-display-content"><div data-pf-type="Accordion3.Flex.Content" class="sc-goWbVR iRUUKk pf-221_"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-222_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-223_"><p class="sc-kUdmUV iejJTZ pf-224_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">1 Flasche Rosmarinwasser (125 ml) + 1 Flasche Rosmarinöl (50 ml) + kostenloser Rasur- und Bartguide von Störtebekker.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></details></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-5660" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-epRwmx cpmRjY pf-226_ pf-color-scheme-1 pf-lg-hide pf-md-hide pf-sm-hide pf-hide"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-djVWQC dKziBg"><div class="sc-tafSX ePbmtR pf-227_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px;position:relative" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-sm:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-pKreJ bIaXH pf-228_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-kOHUsU fHbtje pf-229_ pf-heading-3-h3 new-branding-headline-font moresize grey-font"><span data-pf-